name: Domain of Mastery: Shadowed Legacy II
description:
The corpse of a once prosperous city that later fell into ruin, its enigmatic structure hinting at its future, cut off from remembrance.
If you can destroy the foes that dwell within this place, you may gain insight and enlightenment that could improve your Talents.
disorder: When a character triggers Electro-Charged or Lunar-Charged reactions, a shockwave will be released, dealing AoE DMG. A shockwave can be unleashed once every 5s.
